headline: Is Costco Stock a Buy Now or Still Too Expensive to Touch?
summary: COST trades at 46.21X forward P/E, below its median but above peers, while renewal rates, comps and digital sales stay strong, making it a hold for now.

headline: Dollar General Corporation Announces Webcast of its Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings Conference Call
summary: GOODLETTSVILLE, Tenn., February 12, 2026--Dollar General Corporation (NYSE: DG) today announced that it plans to release its financial results for the fiscal 2025 fourth quarter and full year ended January 30, 2026, on March 12, 2026.
